getSupportingTerms

public List<KAMStoreDaoImpl.BelTerm> getSupportingTerms(Kam.KamNode kamNode,
                                                        boolean removeDuplicates,
                                                        KAMCatalogDao.NamespaceFilter namespaceFilter)
                                                 throws InvalidArgument,
                                                        KamStoreException
Returns a list of BEL term objects which support the KAM node. If removeDuplicates is true, the list of terms returned is reduced to the list of unique terms based on namespace identifiers. If namespaceFilter is set, the list of terms reported is initially filtered with respect to the filter criteria.

getKamNodes

public List<Kam.KamNode> getKamNodes(Kam kam,
                                     FunctionEnum functionType,
                                     KAMStoreDaoImpl.Namespace namespace,
                                     String parameterValue)
                              throws KamStoreException
Find all KAM nodes that match the given function and that were compiled with the given namespace, and parameter value.
This method will not return nodes that were compiled with equivalents of the given namespace and parameter value. Use KamStore.getKamNodes(Kam, FunctionEnum, SkinnyUUID) to search all equivalents.

getKamNodes

public List<Kam.KamNode> getKamNodes(Kam kam,
                                     Kam.KamNode example)
                              throws KamStoreException
Find all KAM nodes that share node parameters with the example KAM node.

For instance, given a kam with the following nodes:

  • complex(p(1), g(2))
  • p(1)
  • g(2)
  • r(2)
  • act(r(2))
Providing the complex(p(1), g(2)) KAM node will yield the following KAM nodes:
  • p(1)
  • g(2)
  • r(2)
  • act(r(2))

Specified by:
getKamNodes in interface KamStore
Parameters:
kam - KAM, the KAM that the nodes are contained within
example - Example KAM node, the KAM node to match on
Returns:
All KAM nodes that share node parameters with node
Throws:
KamStoreException - Thrown if an error occurred retrieving node candidates
